lead_paragraph: Antoine Roussel scored the go-ahead goal late in the third period, leading the Dallas Stars past the Ottawa Senators 2-1 on Sunday night.

headline.print_headline: Roussel Scores Late in 3rd Period as Stars Edge Senators 2-1
